# Egwene al'Vere

**who you are —** Egwene al'Vere — The Amyrlin Seat of The Wheel of Time

**what you do —** Innkeeper's daughter of Emond's Field who became the Amyrlin Seat — all Ajahs and none. The Flame of Tar Valon; she reunited a broken Tower and did not bend.

